    'PH' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Tutohi i te E-tauhokohoko a meake nei i te Philippines me Selldone Pakihi OS</h2>\n\n<p>I te Philippines, kei reira nga maakete hihiri e tutaki ai i nga mahi mamati, kei te whakairohia e Selldone Business OS he huarahi hou mo te hokohoko-e. Ko tenei papaaho-kore-mono he mea whakarite mo nga kaihokohoko Filipino, ka taea e ratou te hoko i nga momo momo hua, ratonga, ohaurunga, tae atu ki nga konae ma te ngawari.</p>\n\n<h3>Whakaahua To Niche Mamati</h3>\n<p>Mo nga pakihi a Filipino, he maamaa ake te whakatu i tetahi tuakiri ipurangi motuhake inaianei. Ma te Selldone, ka uru marie te e-tauhokohoko ki roto i to rohe i whiriwhiria e koe, me te whakapumau i te pono me te whakawhirinaki ki nga manuhiri katoa.</p>\n\n<h3>Q</h3> mo te Kaihokohoko Filipino\n<p>Ko te whakarewanga i tetahi toa ipurangi i Philippines me ngawari. Ko te Selldone ka whakarite ka taea e nga kaihokohoko te whakarite me te iti o te ngangau, te whakakore i te hiahia mo te manaaki, monomai, me nga tauira. Ko nga mea katoa mo te hanga e-tauhokohoko te uru me te ngawari.</p>\n\n<h3>Led with the Philippines' Tax System</h3>\n<p>Na te hohonutanga o te maarama ki te whenua taake o Philippines, ka tuku a Selldone i nga waahanga tatauranga taake whakauru. Ma tenei ka whakarite kia noho ū nga pakihi i te wa e whakatere ana i nga uauatanga o te taake a rohe.</p>\n\n<h3>Scaling with Filipino Ambitions</h3>\n<p>Mai i nga tiimata i Manila ki te whakatipu rama i Cebu, kua hoahoatia a Selldone ki te whanake me koe. Koia te tino hoa e-tauhokohoko mo nga pakihi e whakaaro ana ki te tipu me te angitu.</p>\n\n<h3>Conversion-Centric Approach</h3>\n<p>Selldone ehara i te mea mo te hoko noa; e pā ana ki te whakarite whai wāhitanga katoa tatau. I hangaia ma te whakaaro ki te maakete Filipino, kua arotauhia kia huri nga manuhiri ki te hunga pono.</p>\n\n<h3>Whakauru mo te Kaihokohoko Filipino</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Waehere utu</b> ki te whakanui me te utu i nga kaihoko pono.</li>\n    <li><b>STapaenga Motuhake</b> ki te whakawai i te hunga whakarongo whanui.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Sells and Upsells</b> ki te whakanui i ia tauwhitinga.</li>\n    <li><b>Gift Card Features</b> mo aua waahi koha motuhake.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Automated Marketing Whakaritea mo te Philippines</h3>\n<p>Ko te whakauru i nga kaimakitaki Filipino kanorau he ngawari ki nga taputapu hokohoko waka me nga taputapu whakatairanga a Selldone. Ko te hanga hononga pumau ki te motu.</p>\n\n<h3>Redefining E-tauhokohoko Paerewa</h3>\n<p>Ahakoa ko nga papaaho penei i te WooCommerce he wero mo te manaaki me te wheako kaiwhakamahi kua wehewehea, ko Selldone e tuku ana i te haerenga whakakotahi me te hoa-kaiwhakamahi mo nga kaihokohoko me nga kaihoko.</p>\n\n<h3>SKo nga Paerewa Tuku iho</h3>\n<p>Ko nga papaa-e-tauhokohoko tikanga, penei i te Shopify, Salesforce, Magento ranei, ka haere mai me o raatau momo wero:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Moretanga Momorongo</b> na te tiritiri a te hunga tuatoru.</li>\n    <li><b>Kua pakaru nga monomai</b> ka taea te aukati i te wheako hokohoko.</li>\n    <li><b>Complex Setups</b> me te tini o nga monomai me nga tauira.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone ka whakangawari i tenei, ka tuku ki nga kaihokohoko Filipino he haerenga e-hokohoko ngawari, haumaru, whai hua hoki.</p>\n\n<p>Mo nga kaihokohoko o nga Philippines, Selldone Pakihi OS e tohu ana mo te heke mai o te hokohoko-e. Rukuhia ka wheako i te ngaru e whai ake nei o te pakihi ipurangi.</p>"],
    'PK' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Charting a New E-commerce Era for Pakistan with Selldone Business OS</h2>\n\n<p>Amidst the bustling bazaars and digital transformations of Pakistan, Selldone Business OS is carving a niche in the e-commerce realm. This no-plugin platform is meticulously tailored for Pakistani merchants, offering a holistic solution to sell a myriad of products, services, subscriptions, and even files.</p>\n\n<h3>Carve Your Digital Niche</h3>\n<p>Pakistani businesses are no longer confined to physical boundaries. With Selldone, e-commerce seamlessly integrates into your chosen domain, ensuring authenticity and fostering trust with every online visitor.</p>\n\n<h3>Streamlined Beginnings</h3>\n<p>Initiating an online venture in Pakistan should be devoid of complexities. Selldone ensures that merchants can commence their e-commerce journey with unparalleled ease, sidestepping the hassles of hosting, plugins, and templates.</p>\n\n<h3>Harmonized with Pakistan's Tax Landscape</h3>\n<p>With an intrinsic understanding of Pakistan's tax framework, Selldone integrates a robust tax calculation feature. This ensures businesses operate seamlessly, adhering to local taxation norms without any hitches.</p>\n\n<h3>Scaling with Pakistan's Visionary Brands</h3>\n<p>From emerging startups in Karachi to flourishing brands in Lahore, Selldone is primed to grow in tandem. It's the e-commerce partner for businesses that envision a boundless future.</p>\n\n<h3>Conversion-Centric Approach</h3>\n<p>Selldone transcends mere selling; it's about optimizing every potential opportunity. Crafted with the Pakistani market in mind, it's honed to transform visitors into dedicated customers.</p>\n\n<h3>Engaging Incentives for the Pakistani Shopper</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Discount Codes</b> to celebrate festive shopping sprees.</li>\n    <li><b>Special Offers</b> to allure a diverse audience.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Sells and Upsells</b> to amplify the shopping experience.</li>\n    <li><b>Gift Card Features</b> for those cherished moments of gifting.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Automated Marketing Tailored for Pakistan</h3>\n<p>Engaging the diverse and dynamic Pakistani audience is a cinch with Selldone's built-in auto marketing and campaigns tools. It's about forging enduring connections in this vibrant nation.</p>\n\n<h3>Setting a New E-commerce Benchmark</h3>\n<p>While platforms like WooCommerce might present challenges with hosting and offer a fragmented user experience, Selldone delivers a cohesive and user-friendly journey for both merchants and shoppers.</p>\n\n<h3>Transcending Traditional Platforms</h3>\n<p>Conventional e-commerce platforms, such as Shopify, Salesforce, or Magento, often come bundled with challenges:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Information Risks</b> due to potential third-party sharing.</li>\n    <li><b>Broken Plugins</b> that can disrupt the seamless shopping journey.</li>\n    <li><b>Complex Setups</b> necessitating myriad plugins and templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone simplifies this, offering Pakistani merchants a streamlined, secure, and efficient e-commerce experience.</p>\n\n<p>For the merchants of Pakistan, Selldone Business OS is not just a platform; it's the dawn of a new e-commerce epoch. Embark on this journey and redefine your online business landscape.</p>\n"],
